OL,7,FA dad from Lisburn has called for a
OL,8,Fspecialist mother and baby unit to
OL,9,Ftreat postpartum psychosis after his
OL,10,Ffamily were left with no choice but to
OL,11,Fmeet in hospital staff changing rooms
OL,12,Fwhile his wife was receiving treatment.
OL,14,FGemma Reaney was treated for the
OL,15,Fserious mental health condition in a
OL,16,Fhospital ward for a period of almost
OL,17,Fthree months. It affects around 1,400
OL,18,Fnew mums in the UK each year.
