OL,7,FHer husband, Ross, has spoken to UTV
OL,8,Fabout their family's experience and
OL,9,Ftheir campaign for change.
OL,11,FThe couple welcomed their much loved
OL,12,Flittle girl in December 2023 but
OL,13,Funfortunately their newborn bubble was
OL,14,Fshort-lived.
OL,16,FTwo to three weeks after giving birth,
OL,17,FRoss said Gemma began to act out of
OL,18,Fcharacter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
