OL,7,F"They said they needed to admit Gemma,
OL,8,Fbut it was around two days before
OL,9,Fthere was a space anywhere in the
OL,10,Fcountry to be able to get her into
OL,11,Fhospital and into care," Ross told UTV.
OL,13,F"At that time, I naively didn't think
OL,14,Fit would be something that would take
OL,15,Fa long time to recover from - I was
OL,16,Fhoping it would maybe be a couple of
OL,17,Fdays, maybe a week, but it turned into
OL,18,F91 days."
