OL,7,FGemma was diagnosed with a severe
OL,8,Fdepressive episode that led to
OL,9,Fpsychosis.
OL,11,F"For anyone who doesn't know what
OL,12,Fpsychosis is like, it's basically a
OL,13,Fstranger has taken over the person you
OL,14,Floves body...it is the illness that's
OL,15,Ftaking over, it's no longer the person
OL,16,Fand that's why it's treated as such a
OL,17,Fmedical emergency as they are not in
OL,18,Fcontrol of themselves anymore,"
OL,19,Fexplained Ross.
OL,26,@sD@AOUzD@_O]
