OL,7,FThe mental health ward where Gemma
OL,8,Freceived treatment had no specific
OL,9,Fprovision for mothers and babies.
OL,11,F"It was a very loud, noisy and scary
OL,12,Fplace. There are often other patients
OL,13,Fthere that are aggressive or violent,"
OL,14,Fsaid Ross.
OL,16,F"It's deemed unsafe to bring a baby
OL,17,Finto a normal mental health ward which
OL,18,Fmeant we couldn't do normal visiting.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@fO]xD@AOU
