OL,7,F"Any meetings that did happen took
OL,8,Fplace in a staff changeover room, so
OL,9,Feffectively a staff changing room.
OL,11,F"I think we need mother and baby units
OL,12,Fin this country. There have been talks
OL,13,Fabout interim measures in place but
OL,14,Fit's not enough. Especially in the
OL,15,Ffirst few months of a newborn's life,
OL,16,Fthat's the most important thing, but
OL,17,Fthat was taken away from us."
