OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,8,FHealth told UTV that it remains
OL,9,F"committed to establishing a regional
OL,10,FMother and Baby Unit" adding that an
OL,11,F"outlines business case" was submitted
OL,12,Fby the Belfast Trust in September 2025
OL,13,Fand is "currently under review".
OL,15,FThey continued: "Funding decisions
OL,16,Fwill depend on the outcome of the
OL,17,Fongoing Budget process following the
OL,18,FUK-wide Spending Review.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
