OL,7,F"While we cannot confirm a timeline at
OL,8,Fthis stage, work is progressing and
OL,9,Foptions for interim provision are
OL,10,Fbeing explored."
OL,12,FThe department explained that in the
OL,13,Fmeantime, health trusts have been
OL,14,F"asked to identify 'Safe Areas' within
OL,15,Fthe adult inpatient units where babies
OL,16,Fand children can visit their mothers"
OL,17,Fand that these are "being funded to
OL,18,Fensure they are as family-friendly and
OL,19,Fsupportive as possible".
