OL,7,FWhile Gemma received treatment at the
OL,8,Fhospital, one of the nurses directed
OL,9,FRoss towards a charity called Action
OL,10,Fon Postpartum Psychosis (APP).
OL,12,F"The charity helped me to speak to a
OL,13,Fdad who had been through it and that
OL,14,Fwas the first time I got a sign of
OL,15,Fhope that there was a possibility of
OL,16,Fcoming through it," he said.
OL,18,F"The consultants and staff can't say
OL,19,Fvery much as they can't give you false
OL,20,Fhope, but that also means that you
OL,21,Fdon't really have any hope at all."
