OL,7,F"Gemma is doing amazing, her recovery
OL,8,Fhas gone better than anyone could hope
OL,9,Ffor especially in terms of how severe
OL,10,Fthe illness was at the time.
OL,12,F"She's back at work, and training and
OL,13,Fis really healthy.
OL,15,F"I could not be more proud of her."
